vim-kobito
===

This is Vim plugin for opening file by Kobito(use link file feature).

Requirements
---

- Mac OS
- Kobito version 1.7.0 or later


Usage
---

You can use `KobitoOpen` command.

If you execute `KobitoOpen` with no parameter, kobito.vim open current file.
If you execute `KobitoOpen` with parameter, kobito.vim open the file as parameter.
Parameter can be specified more than one.

```vim
" open current file by Kobito
:KobitoOpen

" open specified file by Kobito
:KobitoOpen /path/to/file

" open specified more than one files by Kobito
:KobitoOpen /path/to/file1 /path/to/file2 /path/to/file3
```

